As Acting Secretary of DHS, Wolf helped orchestrate the cruel practice of separating immigrant children from their families.

@DHS_Wolf is unfit to lead the Department of Homeland Security. 

The Senate must reject his nomination.

We can only be successful in defeating this global pandemic with support from health organizations around the world. 

@WHO is a critical partner in the fight against #coronavirus and @realDonaldTrump's decision to stop funding is reckless and dangerous.
